gomodel:SYNGO_2252  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099060 replaced by GO:0099634" , "Rationale: Fig.2: \"Immunogold analysis of GABAAR α1 and β2 subunit at VP inhibitory synapses in control and stargazer mice.\"\n- \"Likewise, the average density of gold label for the β2 subunit per μm PSD length was 6.40 ± 0.24 for controls and 9.33 ± 0.37 for the stargazer mice, representing a 45.7% increase (Fig. 2D)'\n\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: \"Immunogold analysis of GABAAR α1 and β2 subunit at VP inhibitory synapses in control and stargazer mice.\"" ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-0593-3443" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2286-1587" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-2514-0216" ;
